data.description: Exquisite home located in the Rockwell Place subdivision in Lakemoor with 3 spacious bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, 2 car garage and LARGE FINISHED BASEMENT!  You will truly appreciate the intricate details in this home. Well cared for and loved! This home features a gorgeous layout as you enter from the front door and move throughout. The kitchen opens to the family room which is great for entertaining.  The family room has a gorgeous gas fireplace and cathedral ceilings! The finished basement has all the space you will need for setting up a workout space, entertaining, office and more!  The 2nd floor has a large LOFT that overlooks the 1st floor living space and gives you ample space to utilize.  Great Location! Convenient to Route 120 and many restaurants, shopping and more!  Great Community! Light traffic and gorgeous sunset views from the large and spacious back yard!
